990s%20were%20a%20period%20of%20higher%20productivity%20growth%20and%20underestimated%20growth%2C%20starting%20the%20year%20at%202%25%20but%20ending%20closer%20to%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fpu1Of%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22GDP%20growth%20projections%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20historical%20examples%20are%20worth%20thinking%20about%20today%20because%20growth%20expectations%20are%20climbing.%20Blue%20Chip%20consensus%20expectations%20for%202024%20real%20GDP%20have%20jumped%2C%20tripling%20since%20last%20summer%2C%20to%202.1%25%20from%200.7%25%20in%20June.%20Unsurprisingly%2C%20recession%20fears%20have%20collapsed.%20Professional%20forecasters%20now%20see%20just%20a%2023.9%25%20chance%20of%20a%20drop%20in%20real%20GDP%20in%20the%20next%20quarter%2C%20down%20from%20nearly%2050%25%20this%20time%20last%20year.%20If%20we're%20seeing%20a%20genuine%20increase%20in%20productivity%2C%20the%20takeaway%20is%20that%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20be%20fleeting.%20If%20the%20past%20is%20prologue%2C%20the%20consensus%20will%20consistently%20be%20revising%20up%20growth%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20AI%20boom%20isn't%20here%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0yet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20is%20littered%20with%20discussions%20about%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tackling-jobs-humans-dont-have-time-for-or-want-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20going%20to%20send%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20hyperspeed.%20But%20it's%20probably%20too%20soon%20to%20be%20thinking%20about%20these%20factors%20as%20the%20main%20driver%20of%20recent%20productivity%20growth.%20That's%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20productivity%20paradox.%20Productivity%20miracles%20don't%20ne