ffect%20immediately%20after%20that.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20various%20policies%20and%20schemes%20of%20the%20government%2C%20the%20message%20sent%20by%20the%20ministry%20also%20asked%20for%20feedback%20and%20suggestions%20from%20the%20recipients.%20The%20handle%20from%20which%20the%20messages%20were%20sent%20-%20which%20has%20a%20green%20tick%20-%20describes%20itself%20as%3A%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Bharat%20Sampark%20is%20an%20ongoing%20initiative%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20for%20evaluation%20of%20the%20flagship%20schemes%20and%20improvement%20in%20its%20implementation%20and%20delivery.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20states%20MeitY's%20address%20and%20has%20a%20link%20to%20its%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC's%20latest%20action%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20directions%20to%20the%20chief%20electoral%20officer%20of%20Karnataka%20to%20take%20action%20against%20Union%20Minister%20Shobha%20Karandlaje%2C%20based%20on%20the%20DMK's%20complaint%2C%20over%20her%20alleged%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20people%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20panel%20had%20also%20ordered%20the%20cabinet%20secretary%2C%20chief%20secretaries%20of%20all%20states%2C%20and%20chief%20electoral%20offficers%20to%20remove%20all%20unauthorised%20political%20advertisements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actions%20are%20being%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar's%20statement%20while%20announcing%20the%20election%20dates%20that%20the%20poll%20panel%20will%20do%20everything%20in%20its%20power%20to%20combat%20four%20'Ms'%20-%20muscle%2C%20money%2C%20misinformation%20and%20MCC%20violations%20-%20that%20can%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20free-and-fair%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711012860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2F51qsbfd_election-commission-reuters_625x300_05_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-asks