al-debt-releif-mistake-mohela-retirement-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStudent-loan%20forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20on%20the%20way%20for%20thousands%20more%20borrowers%20who%20have%20worked%20in%20public%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20White%20House%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20be%20canceling%20nearly%20%246%20billion%20in%20student%20debt%20for%2078%2C000%20borrowers%20in%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program%2C%20which%20forgiveness%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20press%20release%20from%20the%20Education%20Department%2C%20this%20latest%20batch%20of%20relief%20results%20from%20fixes%20to%20PSLF%2C%20including%20borrowers%20who%20benefited%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpublic-service-loan-forgiveness-program-major-overhaul-student-debt-biden-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimited-time%20waiver%20that%20expired%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20allow%20past%20payments%20that%20previously%20didn't%20qualify%20for%20relief%20to%20count%20toward%20forgiveness%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20too%20long%2C%20our%20nation's%20teachers%2C%20nurses%2C%20social%20workers%2C%20firefighters%2C%20and%20other%20public%20servants%20faced%20logistical%20troubles%20and%20trap%20doors%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20access%20the%20debt%20relief%20they%20were%20entitled%20to%20under%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWith%20this%20announcement%2C%20the%20Biden-Harris%20Administration%20is%20showing%20how%20we're%20taking%20further%20steps%20not%20only%20to%20fix%20those%20trap%20doors%2C%20but%20also%20to%20expand%20opportunity%20to%20many%20more%20Americans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20more%20than%20100%20times%20more%20borrowers%20are%20eligible%20for%20PSLF%20than%20there%20were%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Cardona%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20will%20email%20impacted%20borrowers%20next%20week%20to%20congratulate%20them%20on%20their%20relief.%20Biden%20will%20also%20email%20an%20additional%20380%2C000%20borrowers%20in%20public%20service%20who%20are%20within%20one%20or%20two%20years%20of%20loan%20forgiveness%20through%20PSLF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20continue%20your%20career%20in%20public%20service%2C%20you're%20on%20track%20to%20get%20your%20eligible%20student%20loans%20forgiven%20in%20less%20than%20two%20years%20through%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20version%20of%20Biden's%20letter%2C%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20administration%20official%20told%20reporters%20on%20a%20Wednesday%20press%20call%20that%20Biden%20is%20directly%20communicating%20with%20borrowers%20because%20he%20wants%20them%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20benefits%20PSLF%20can%20offer%2C%20along%20with%20the%20impacts%20debt%20relief%20can%20have%20on%20Americans%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20relief%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20a%20range%20of%20targeted%20actions%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20implemented%20over%20the%20past%20year%20to%20get%20more%20relief%20to%20borrowers.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20department%20announced%20in%20February%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-debt-cancellation-save-income-driven-payment-plan-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E153%2C000%20borrowers%20would%20get%20%241.2%20billion%20in%20debt%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20result%20of%20a%20new%20provision%20of%20the%20new%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%20that%20shortens%20the%20timeline%20for%20borrowers%20to%20see%20debt%20cancellation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20many%20other%20borrowers%20are%20struggling%20to%20navigate%20the%20return%20to%20repayment%20that%20began%20in%20October%20after%20an%20over%20three-year%20payment%20pause.%20The%20Education%20Department%20found%20that%20all%20four%20major%20federal%20student-loan%20servicers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-companies-education-department-punishment-borrowers-repayment-errors-billing-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efailed%20to%20send%20on-time%20billing%20statements%20to%20borrowers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it%20released%20an%20accountability%20framework%20in%20December%20to%20ensure%20oversight%20over%20the%20servicers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loans-easier-repayment-biden-budget-request-borrowers-cheaper-college-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrained%20funding%20at%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20leaving%20both%20borrowers%20and%20servicers%20without%20the%20resources%20they%20need%20to%20navigate%20the%20return%20to%20repayment%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20is%20also%20in%20the%20process%20of%20implementing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-will-take-cancel-student-debt-higher-education-act-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroader%20form%20of%20debt%20relief%20using%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20of%201965%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20its%20second%20try%20at%20relief%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20its%20first%20plan%20down.%20The%20department%20is%20expected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loans-where-does-biden-debt-cancellation-stand-negotiations-relief-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelease%20a%20draft%20text%20for%20the%20new%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDid%20you%20receive%20student-loan%20forgiveness%3F%20Share%20your%20story%20with%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3