ad%20approached%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20restrain%20the%20Centre%20from%20notifying%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provision%20for%20a%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20was%20part%20of%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021%2C%20brought%20by%20the%20Centre%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20rules%2C%20if%20this%20unit%20comes%20across%20or%20is%20informed%20about%20any%20posts%20that%20are%20fake%2C%20false%2C%20and%20contain%20misleading%20facts%20about%20the%20business%20of%20the%20government%2C%20it%20would%20flag%20them%20to%20social%20media%20intermediaries.%20Once%20such%20a%20post%20is%20flagged%2C%20the%20intermediary%20has%20the%20option%20of%20taking%20it%20down%20or%20putting%20a%20disclaimer.%20In%20taking%20the%20second%20option%2C%20the%20intermediary%20risks%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20had%20expressed%20concerns%20of%20censorship%20and%20said%20the%20new%20rules%20would%20restrict%20users%20from%20expressing%20themselves%20freely%20on%20social%20media.%20They%20had%20said%20the%20social%20media%20intermediaries%20would%20readily%20remove%20posts%20flagged%20by%20the%20government's%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20to%20avoid%20legal%20troubles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamra%20also%20challenged%20the%20new%20IT%20rules%20for%20violating%20his%20right%20to%20work%20as%20a%20political%20satirist%20and%20expressed%20fear%20of%20losing%20his%20social%20media%20access%20if%20his%20content%20is%20flagged%20by%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit.%20The%20rules%20will%20allow%20the%20government%20to%20flag%20any%20content%20critical%20of%20its%20policies%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20responded%20that%20the%20rules%20were%20issued%20in%20public%20interest%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20fake%20news.%20It%20had%20also%20said%20the%20fact-check%20will%20be%20based%20on%20evidence%20and%20such%20decisions%20can%20be%20challenged%20in%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20also%20said%20political%20opinions%2C%20satire%20and%20comedy%20are%20not%20linked%20to%20government%20business%3B%20the%20petitioners%20have%20argued%20that%20'business%20of%20the%20Central%20Government'%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bvague%26quot%3B%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2011%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20refused%20to%20grant%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20setting%20up%20the%20Fact-Check%20Unit%2C%20noting%20that%20no%20grave%20and%20irreparable%20loss%20would%20be%20caused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20single-judge%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20petitioners%20fear%20that%20exchange%20of%20information%20in%20the%20form%20of%20political%20discourses%20or%20comments%2C%20political%20satire%2C%20and%20so%20on%20may%20be%20targeted%20if%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20is%20notified.%20However%2C%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20has%20said%20the%20unit%20only%20intends%20to%20deal%20with%20government%20business%20in%20its%20strict%20sense%2C%20and%20did%20not%20aim%20to%20muzzle%20political%20views%2C%20satire%20or%20sarcasm%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitions%20against%20the%20new%20IT%20Rules%20were%20referred%20to%20a%20single-judge%20bench%20after%20a%20division%20bench's%20split%20verdict%20in%20January.%20While%20one%20of%20the%20judges%20on%20the%20division%20bench%20had%20struck%20down%20the%20rules%2C%20terming%20them%20unconstitutional%2C%20another%20had%20upheld%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20it%20would%20not%20notify%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20until%20a%20final%20verdict%20on%20IT%20rules.%20But%20after%20the%20split%20verdict%2C%20the%20Centre%20said%20the%20oral%20assurance%20could%20be%20extended%20only%20until%20the%20third%20judge%20took%20up%20the%20matter.%20The%20petitioners%20had%20then%20filed%20interim%20applications%2C%20seeking%20a%20pause%20on%20notifying%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit.%C2%A0After%20getting%20no%20relief%20from%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20the%20petitioners%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711011480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fe8bgk2vo_supreme-court-getty_625x300_31_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-puts-on-hold-centres-notification-on-its-fact-check-unit-5281535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20the%20Centre%20notified%20the%20fact%20check%20unit%20under%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20to%20%26quot%3Baddress%20the%20challenge%20of%20fake%20news%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20paused%20the%20notification%2C%20setting%20aside%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court's%20go-ahead%20to%20the%20government's%20move.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-puts-on-hold-centres-notification-on-its-fact-check-unit-5281535%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-puts-on-hold-centres-notification-on-its-fact-check-unit-5281535%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-puts-on-hold-centres-notification-on-its-fact-check-unit-5281535%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nigeria%20president%20bans%20foreign%20trips%20for%20officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711010876000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F11875%2Fproduction%2F_132979717_gettyimages-1803979403-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68615355%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20three-month%20prohibition%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20cut%20government%20spending%20amid%20a%20cost-of-living%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonica