0and%20said%20the%20party%20is%20seeking%20to%20create%20an%20alibi%20in%20%26quot%3Butter%20desperation%20over%20its%20imminent%20defeat%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20we%20are%20taking%20up%20today%20is%20extremely%20serious.%20This%20issue%20affects%20not%20just%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20but%20our%20democracy%20itself%2C%20most%20fundamentally.%20%C2%A0A%20systematic%20effort%20is%20underway%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20cripple%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20financially.%20Funds%20collected%20from%20the%20public%20are%20being%20frozen%20and%20money%20from%20our%20accounts%20is%20being%20taken%20away%20forcibly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Congress%20president's%20statement%20was%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20party's%20claim%20last%20month%20that%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20had%20frozen%20Rs%20115%20crore%20in%20its%20bank%20accounts%20following%20a%20tax%20demand%20of%20Rs%20210%20crore%20as%20dues%20and%20penalty%20for%20the%20financial%20year%202018-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Ajay%20Maken%20alleged%20that%20Rs%2065%20crore%20had%20been%20withdrawn%20by%20the%20department%20from%20three%20of%20the%20party's%20accounts%20even%20though%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20claim%20was%20being%20heard%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20tribunal%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-delhi-high-court-setback-congress-to-appeal-in-supreme-court-in-over-rs-100-crore-pending-tax-case-5230740%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20accept%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20party's%20petition%20to%20stop%20the%20department's%20action%20against%20its%20bank%20accounts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20even%20under%20these%20most%20challenging%20circumstances%2C%20we%20are%20doing%20our%20very%20best%20to%20maintain%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20our%20election%20campaign.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20there%20is%20the%20electoral%20bond%20issue%2C%20which%20has%20been%20declared%20unconstitutional%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20electoral%20bonds%20have%20benefited%2C%20as%20everyone%20knows%2C%20the%20BJP%20hugely%2C%20massively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20finances%20of%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%2C%20are%20under%20a%20determined%20assault.%20This%2C%20we%20all%20believe%2C%20is%20unprecedented%20and%20undemocratic%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Thursday's%20press%20conference%2C%20Mr%20Maken%20said%20in%20Hindi%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bassault%26quot%3B%20on%20Congress'%20bank%20accounts%20was%20an%20attack%20on%20democracy.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%20is%20completely%20financially%20crippled%20and%20can't%20spend%20on%20publicity%2C%20on%20its%20campaign%20and%20can't%20give%20money%20to%20its%20candidates%2C%20then%20why%20are%20the%20elections%20being%20held%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Maken%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20use%20Rs%20285%20crore%20lying%20in%20its%20accounts%20and%20had%20also%20received%20a%20new%20notice%20last%20week%20pertaining%20to%20the%20year%201994-95.%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20rate%2C%20they%20will%20go%20back%20to%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20time%2C%20when%20Jamnalal%20Bajaj%20was%20the%20treasurer%2C%20and%20cull%20out%20something%20to%20send%20us%20a%20notice%20about%20and%20freeze%20our%20accounts%20before%20the%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Ability%20To%20Fight%20Damaged'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20Congress'%20financial%20identity%20was%20%E2%80%9Cerased%E2%80%9D%20a%20month%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20been%20done%20literally%20two%20months%20before%20the%20election.%20One%20notice%20comes%20from%20the%2090s%2C%20one%20from%20six-seven%20years%20ago.%20Quantum%20amount%3F%20Rs%2014%20lakh.%20And%20punishment%3F%20Our%20entire%20financial%20identity%E2%80%A6%20Already%2C%20our%20ability%20to%20fight%20the%20election%20has%20been%20damaged.%20We%20have%20already%20lost%20a%20month.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20criminal%20action%20on%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20this%20a%20criminal%20action%20done%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Home%20minister%2C%20it%20is%20very%20clear.%20This%20type%20of%20activity%20does%20not%20happen%20without%20them%20in%20today's%20India...%20This%20has%20been%20orchestrated%20to%20cripple%20us%20in%20the%20elections.%20And%20no%20court%20is%20saying%20anything.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20isn't%20saying%20anything.%20No%20institution%20is%20saying%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20controversy%20over%20his%20%26quot%3Bshakti%26quot%3B%20remark%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20fighting%20against%20hatred-filled%20%3Cem%3E'asura-shakti'%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%20During%20a%20rally%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20had%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20fighting%20against%20a%20shakti%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20not%20talking%20about%20a%20religious%20power%20but%20the%20shakti%20of%20corruption%20and%20falsehood.%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20several%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20had%2C%20however%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20insulting%20Hinduism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711010580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6ld89glc_sonia-gandhi-rahul-gandhi-ani_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsystematic-effort-by-pm-to-cripple-congress-financially-sonia-gandhi-5281139%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Levelling%