3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20told%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20to%20immediately%20stop%20sending%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20messages%20on%20WhatsApp.%20The%20ministry%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Feci-backend%2Fpublic%2Fapi%2Fdownload%3Furl%3DLMAhAK6sOPBp%252FNFF0iRfXbEB1EVSLT41NNLRjYNJJP1KivrUxbfqkDatmHy12e%252FzBiU51zPFZI5qMtjV1qgjFjVCLfCrR65PIpVS5CsMV%252FGVTR3%252B6uhrbgZprhECh1UHCSv%252B1yJkuMeCkTzY9fhBvw%253D%253D%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20EC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthough%20the%20letters%20were%20sent%20out%20before%20MCC%20%5BModel%20Code%20of%20Conduct%5D%20period%2C%20but%20due%20to%20system%20architecture%20and%20network%20limitations%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20some%20letters%20have%20a%20delayed%20delivery%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Commission%20has%20received%20complaints%20from%20various%20quarters%20that%20such%20messages%20are%20still%20being%20delivered%20on%20citizens%E2%80%99%20phones.%20Since%20the%20MCC%20is%20now%20in%20force%2C%20you%20are%20hereby%20directed%20to%20ensure%20forthwith%20that%20no%20further%20delivery%20of%20%E2%80%98WhatsApp%20messages%E2%80%99%20take%20place%20during%20MCC%20period.%20A%20compliance%20report%20in%20this%20regard%20may%20be%20sent%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20EC%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20notice%20does%20not%20say%20that%20any%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20on%20the%20messages%20already%20sent%20after%20the%20MCC%20was%20already%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprima-facie-mcc-violation-chandigarh-authorities-refer-modis-mass-whatsapp-message-to-ec%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20Chandigarh%20election%20authorities%20had%20said%20that%20the%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20being%20send%20in%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20were%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprima%20facie%20violation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20MCC%2C%20and%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20EC%20given%20its%20all-India%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20relates%20to%20the%20circulation%20of%20bulk%20messages%20to%20millions%20of%20Indians%20on%20WhatsApp%20from%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%20Sampark%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20a%20letter%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20attached.%20The%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Sampark%20account%20had%20the%20registered%20office%20address%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELargely%20highlighting%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20past%20ten%20years%2C%20Modi%20in%20the%20letter%20stated%20that%20transformation%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20was%20the%20biggest%20achievement%20of%20his%20government.%20He%20then%20sought%20people%E2%80%99s%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711008890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19115117%2FScreenshot-2024-03-19-at-8.22.50-AM-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-tells-it-ministry-to-immediately-stop-sending-viksit-bharat-messages-with-modis-letter%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ministry%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20messages%20were%20meant%20to%20go%20out%20before%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20was%20in%20place%2C%20but%20were%20delivered%20late%20because%20of%20a%20system%20error.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-tells-it-ministry-to-immediately-stop-sending-viksit-bharat-messages-with-modis-letter%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20The%20Rohingya%20Crisis%20And%20India's%20Stance%20On%20Those%20Seeking%20Asylum%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20being%20a%20developing%20nation%20with%20the%20highest%20population%20globally%2C%20should%20prioritise%20its%20own%20citizens%2C%20the%20Centre%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20while%20underscoring%20concerns%20regarding%20national%20security%20due%20to%20the%20illegal%20entry%20and%20stay%20of%20Rohingya%20refugees.%20This%20declaration%20came%20in%20response%20to%20a%20court%20petition%20urging%20the%20release%20of%20Rohingya%20refugees%20detained%20for%20alleged%20violations%20of%20the%20Foreigners%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohingya%20crisis%20is%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%20that%20has%20drawn%20international%20attention%20due%20to%20its%20magnitude%20and%20complexity.%20Originating%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20Rohingya%20people%20have%20faced%20decades%20of%20persecution%20and%20violence%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20mass%20exodus%20from%20their%20homeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohingya%2C%20primarily%20Muslims%2C%20have%20fled%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20predominantly%20Buddhist%20Myanmar%2C%20seeking%20refuge%20in%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Are%20The%20Rohingya%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohingya%20are%20a%20Muslim%20ethnic%20minority%20group%20residing%20in%20predominantly%20Buddhist%20Myanmar.%20According%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20despite%20living%20in%20the%20country%20for%20generations%2C%20they%20have%20been%20systematically%20denied%20citizenship%20since%201982%2C%20rendering%20them%20stateless%20and%20without%20basic%20rights.%20The%20term%20%26quot%3BRohingya%26quot%3B%20emerged%20in%20the%201950s%20as%20a%20means%20for%20the%20community%20to%20assert%20its%20collective%20identity%20and%20historical%20ties%20to%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoots%20Of%20The%20Crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecades%20of%20discrimination%20and%20marginalisation%20against%20the%20Rohingya%20by%20the%20Myanmar%20government%20have%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20UN's%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20said%20in%20a%20report.%20Restrictive%20citizenship%20laws%2C%20imposed%20limitations%20on%20marriage%2C%20family%20planning%2C%20education%2C%20and%20freedom%20of%20movement%20have%20compounded%20the%20community's%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Rohingya%20refugee%20rescued%20at%20sea.%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20Rohingya%20refugee%20rescued%20at%20sea.%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fr40aukqg_rohingya-afp_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Rohingya%20refugee%20rescued%20at%20sea.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakhine%20State%2C%20where%20most%20Rohingya%20reside%2C%20is%20Myanmar's%20least%20developed%20region%2C%20and%20a%20constant%20flashpoint%20in%20tensions%20between%20the%20Rohingya%20and%20other%20ethnic%20groups.%20The%20state's%20capital%20Sittwe%20is%20located%20nearly%20650%20kilometres%20from%20Myanmar's%20capital%20Napyidaw.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEscalation%20Of%20Violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20escalated%20dramatically%20in%20August%202017%20when%20the%20Arakan%20Rohingya%20Salvation%20Army%20(ARSA)%2C%20a%20Rohingya%20insurgent%20group%2C%20launched%20attacks%20on%20Myanmar%20police%20and%20army%20posts%20in%20Rakhine%20State.%20In%20response%2C%20Myanmar's%20military%20launched%20a%20brutal%20crackdown%2C%20characterised%20by%20widespread%20violence%2C%20mass%20killings%2C%20and%20the%20torching%20of%20Rohingya%20villages.%20Hundreds%20of%20thousands%20fled%20across%20the%20border%20into%20neighbouring%20Bangladesh%20to%20escape%20the%20atrocities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20community%20has%20condemned%20Myanmar's%20actions%2C%20with%20many%20labelling%20it%20as%20ethnic%20cleansing%20and%20even%20genocide.%20The%20United%20Nations%2C%20human%20rights%20organisations%2C%20and%20individual%20countries%20have%20called%20for%20accountability%20and%20justice%20for%20the%20Rohingya.%20Legal%20actions%20have%20been%20pursued%20at%20international%20courts%2C%20including%20cases%20at%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(ICJ)%20and%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20(ICC).%20Sanctions%20have%20been%20imposed%20on%20Myanmar's%20military%20leaders%20by%20various%20nations%20and%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERefugee%20Crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20Rohingya%20refugees%20have%20sought%20shelter%20in%20overcrowded%20camps%20in%20Cox's%20Bazaar%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20living%20conditions%20in%20these%20camps%20are%20dire%2C%20often%20made%20worse%20by%20the%20annual%20monsoon%20season%2C%20which%20brings%20flooding%20and%20landslides.%20Disease%20outbreaks%20and%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20basic%20necessities%20pose%20significant%20challenges%20to%20the%20well-being%20of%20Rohingya%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2Fnkdm3mm_rohingyas-in-bangladesh-afp_625x300_25_August_19.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kutupalong%20camp%20In%20Cox's%20Bazaar%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20refugee%20camp%2C%20even%20bigger%20than%20the%20Um%20Rakuba%20camp%20in%20Sudan%20and%20the%20Za'atari%20camp%20in%20Jordan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegional%20Dynamics%20And%20India's%20Stance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohingya%20crisis%20has%20regional%20implications%2C%20with%20refugees%20seeking%20asylum%20in%20neighbouring%20countries%20such%20as%20India%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20Thailand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202019%20report%20by%20the%20US%20think%20tank%20Council%20On%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20approximately%2018%2C000%20Rohingya%20refugees%20have%20officially%20registered%20with%20the%20UN%20refugee%20agency%2C%20but%20Indian%20authorities%20estimate%20that%20the%20total%20Rohingya%20population%20in%20the%20country%20stands%20at%20around%2040%2C000.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20been%20actively%20pursuing%20their%20repatriation.%20Since%20late%202018%2C%20India%20has%20reportedly%20deported%20numerous%20refugees%20back%20to%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Rohingya%20refugee%20looks%20on%20aboard%20a%20National%20Search%20and%20Rescue%20Agency%20(BASARNAS)%20vessel%20after%20they%20were%20rescued%20from%20their%20capsized%20boat%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20Rohingya%20refugee%20looks%20on%20aboard%20a%20National%20Search%20and%20Rescue%20Agency%20(BASARNAS)%20vessel%20after%20they%20were%20rescued%20from%20their%20capsized%20boat%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fs2chns88_rohingya-afp_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Rohingya%20refugee%20looks%20on%20aboard%20a%20National%20Search%20and%20Rescue%20Agency%20(BASARNAS)%20vessel%20after%20they%20were%20rescued%20from%20their%20capsized%20boat%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20Rohingya%20have%20also%20been%20cited%20in%20debates%20regarding%20the%20Centre's%20handling%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA).%20The%20CAA%20aims%20to%20grant%20citizenship%20to%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20excluding%20Muslims%2C%20who%20fled%20religious%20persecution%20and%20entered%20India%20before%202015.%20Responding%20to%20criticism%20from%20the%20Opposition%20regarding