cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTraumatised%20By%20This%26quot%3B%3A%20DNA%20Tests%20Reveal%20Shocking%20Levels%20Of%20Incest%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDNA%20test%20is%20generally%20used%20to%20determine%20the%20ancestry.%20But%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20has%20revealed%20a%20disturbing%20trend%3A%20That%20incest%20is%20far%20more%20common%20in%20the%20country%20than%20many%20think.%20Widespread%20genetic%20testing%20has%20uncovered%20many%20cases%20of%20children%20born%20to%20close%20biological%20relatives%2C%20providing%20an%20unprecedented%20accounting%20of%20incest%20in%20the%20society.%20A%20research%20published%20in%20a%20psychiatry%20text%20book%20in%201975%20put%20the%20rate%20of%20children%20born%20of%20incest%20at%20one%20in%20a%20million.%20But%20recent%20studies%20have%20shown%20the%20number%20has%20reached%20one%20in%207%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20Victoria%20Hill%2C%20who%20discovered%20the%20disturbing%20truth%20through%20a%20DNA%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20started%20talking%20about%20her%20family%20tree%20with%20an%20ex-boyfriend%20at%20their%20high%20school%20reunion%20after%20she%20had%20taken%20a%20DNA%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20were%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20their%20family%20make-up%20was%20similar%2C%20so%20the%20man%20also%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20same%20test.%20Ms%20Hill%20then%20received%20a%20text%20message%20confirming%20her%20worst%20fear%20-%20she%20was%20his%20sister.%20And%20her%20father%20was%20not%20her%20biological%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20traumatised%20by%20this.%20Now%20I'm%20looking%20at%20pictures%20of%20people%20thinking%2C%20well%2C%20if%20he%20could%20be%20my%20sibling%2C%20anybody%20could%20be%20my%20sibling%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2Fus%2Ffertility-fraud-accidental-incest-invs%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Eshe%20told%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20got%20to%20know%20that%20she%20had%20many%20more%20siblings%20that%20just%20the%20brother%20she%20grew%20up%20with%20-%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20slept%20with%20my%20half-sibling.%20I%20went%20to%20elementary%20school%20with%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%20highlighted%20her%20case%20to%20uncover%20something%20called%20an%20accidental%20incest%2C%20which%20proliferated%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20cases%20emerged%20because%20some%20people%20donated%20their%20sperm%20to%20help%20women%20conceive.%20The%20story%20that%20really%20put%20fertility%20fraud%20on%20the%20national%20radar%20was%20that%20of%20Dr%20Donald%20Cline%2C%20who%20fathered%20at%20least%2090%20children%20in%20Indiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabies%20born%20as%20a%20result%20of%20incest%20are%20at%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20having%20birth%20defects%20and%20genetic%20disorders.%20These%20identities%20are%20confirmed%20by%20third%20party%20tests%20that%20look%20for%20homozygosity%2C%20or%20ROH%20for%20short%2C%20which%20reveals%20chunks%20of%20identical%20genetic%20material%20in%20the%20DNA.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711005900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7t2ps6ng_dna-test-unsplash_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftraumatised-by-this-dna-tests-reveal-shocking-levels-of-incest-in-us-5281424%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Babies%20born%20as%20a%20result%20of%20incest%20are%20at%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20having%20birth%20defects%20and%20genetic%20disorders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftraumatised-by-this-dna-tests-reveal-shocking-levels-of-incest-in-us-5281424%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.n