f%20the%20two%20brothers%20brutally%20murdered%20in%20their%20own%20home%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-didnt-do-anything-video-of-brother-of-killer-in-up-double-murder-case-emerges-5281004%5C%22%3EBudaun%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20revealed%20horrific%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20attacked%20on%20the%20neck%2C%20both%20Aayush%20(11)%20and%20Ahaan%20(6)%20were%20stabbed%20multiple%20times%20with%20a%20sharp%20weapon%20on%20their%20back%2C%20chest%20and%20legs.%20According%20to%20the%20post-mortem%20report%2C%20the%20wounds%20on%20their%20legs%20suggest%20the%20children%20may%20have%20attempted%20to%20escape%2C%20only%20to%20be%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20attacker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Sajid%2C%20a%20familiar%20face%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20who%20ran%20a%20barber%20shop%20opposite%20the%20victims'%20residence%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20double%20murder.%20Sajid%2C%20known%20to%20the%20children's%20father%2C%20Vinod%20Singh%2C%20visited%20their%20house%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20borrowing%20Rs%205%2C000.%20However%2C%20moments%20after%20being%20handed%20the%20money%2C%20Sajid%20launched%20a%20savage%20assault%20on%20the%20children%20as%20their%20mother%20prepared%20tea%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20gaining%20entry%20into%20the%20household%2C%20Sajid%20allegedly%20asked%20Aayush%20to%20take%20him%20to%20his%20mother's%20beauty%20salon%20upstairs.%20Upon%20reaching%20the%20second%20floor%2C%20Sajid%20allegedly%20switched%20off%20the%20lights%20before%20launching%20a%20vicious%20assault%20on%20Aayush%20with%20a%20knife.%20As%20Sajid%20slashed%20Aayush's%20throat%2C%20his%20younger%20brother%20Ahaan%20entered%20the%20room.%20Sajid%20then%20grabbed%20Ahaan%20and%20stabbed%20him%20multiple%20times%20as%20well.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20targeted%20their%20other%20sibling%2C%20Piyush%2C%20though%20the%20seven-year-old%20managed%20to%20escape%2C%20susta