des%20to%20come%2C%20those%20who%20are%20less%20dependent%20on%20high%20energy%20and%20consumption%20lifestyles%20will%20also%20be%20better%20placed%20to%20deal%20with%20unpredictabilities%20in%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteer%20with%20environmental%20groups%20and%20communities%2C%20activists%20and%20providers%20of%20aid%2C%20strategists%20and%20workers.%20Multiple%20responses%20are%20required%2C%20which%20include%20working%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20blame%20yourself%20or%20others%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReducing%20our%20complex%20global%20crisis%2C%20born%20of%20very%20deep%20cultural%20roots%2C%20to%20finger-pointing%20based%20on%20facile%20reasonings%20will%20not%20begin%20to%20help%20anyone.%20Least%20of%20all%2C%20yourself.%20While%20we%20can%20hold%20people%20accountable%20for%20their%20decisions%2C%20it%20also%20helps%20to%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20our%20global%20predicament%20is%20not%20created%20by%20any%20one%20generation%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20nation%2C%20family%2C%20or%20person.%20Every%20one%20of%20us%20sits%20atop%20multilayered%20histories%20that%20inform%20our%20perceptions%20of%20the%20world%20and%20define%20our%20options%20within%20it.%20No%20one%20has%20the%20sole%20power%20to%20fix%20the%20past%20or%20the%20present.%20Everything%20is%20more%20complicated%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20expect%20%E2%80%98purity%E2%80%99%20of%20thought%20or%20action%20from%20yourself%20or%20anyone%20else%20who%20cares%20about%20the%20environment.%20Every%20one%20of%20us%20abounds%20in%20contradictions.%20None%20of%20us%20has%20perfect%20will%20or%20judgment%20or%20knowledge%20or%20even%20freedom%20of%20action%20in%20every%20sphere%20of%20our%20lives.%20We%20all%20do%20things%20that%20someone%20else%20will%20judge%20as%20hypocritical.%20Remember%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20all%20fighting%20different%20battles%20too.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20shame%20others%20for%20not%20doing%20exactly%20as%20you%E2%80%99re%20able%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccept%20that%20nothing%20you%20do%20will%20be%20enough.%20You%20alone%20cannot%20stop%20global%20warming%20or%20save%20the%20world.%20Nor%20is%20the%20goal%20to%20prove%20yourself%20an%20individual%20environmental%20hero.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20participate%20in%20local%20and%20global%20changes%20collectively%20driving%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20toward%20a%20more%20equitable%20and%20sustainable%20human%20enterprise.%20Like%20everyone%20else%2C%20you%20can%20only%20do%20your%20best%3B%20some%20days%20and%20some%20choices%20will%20be%20much%20harder%20than%20others.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20others%20shame%20you%20into%20doing%20less%20or%20more%20than%20you%E2%80%99re%20able%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20dream%20of%20utopias.%20Human%20beings%20aren%E2%80%99t%20capable%20of%20creating%20utopias.%20Such%20fantasies%20are%20anti-human%20and%20have%20often%20proven%20dangerous%20to%20attempt.%20But%20as%20individuals%2C%20as%20societies%2C%20as%20a%20species%2C%20we%20can%20certainly%20acknowledge%20that%20there%20have%20been%20times%20and%20places%20when%20we%E2%80%99ve%20lived%20more%20harmoniously%20and%20carefully.%20There%20are%20also%20times%20when%20we%20annihilate%20other%20people%20or%20species%20thoughtlessly%20or%20even%20fanatically.%20All%20these%20capacities%20are%20within%20us.%20Yet%20we%20can%20play%20our%20part%20in%20moving%20society%20toward%20its%20better%20self.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20us%20will%20at%20best%20be%20part%20of%20a%20changing%20tide%2C%20in%20our%20own%20way%2C%20for%20massive%20changes%20that%20will%20take%20years%20or%20generations%20to%20become%20fully%20established%E2%80%94if%20we%E2%80%99re%20lucky.%20And%20if%20we%E2%80%99re%20successful%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20find%20our%20way%20toward%20envisioning%20alternative%20futures%2C%20rediscovering%20how%20to%20build%20communities%20of%20cooperation%20and%20mutual%20aid%2C%20and%20facing%20the%20challenges%20with%20openness%20and%20good%20humour.%20It%20begins%20and%20ends%20with%20understanding%20what%E2%80%99s%20real%20and%20practicing%20compassion%20with%20others%20and%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUsha%20Alexander%20trained%20in%20science%20and%20anthropology.%20After%20working%20for%20years%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20now%20lives%20in%20Gurugram.%20She%E2%80%99s%20written%20two%20novels%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0The%20Legend%20of%20Virinara%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Only%20the%20Eyes%20Are%20Mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711005302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21114724%2FSmallestCliff_2021_AraavaliBiodiversityPark-VijayDhasmana.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fwhat-can-i-do-about-climate-change%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rather%20than%20imagine%20that%20any%20individual%20can%20do%20something%20to%20slow%20down%20climate%20change%20and%20other%20ecocide%2C%20it%20seems%20most%20useful%20to%20first%20orient%20ourselves%20toward%20a%20broadly%20conceived%20vision%20of%20a%20more%20equitable%20and%20less%20consumerist%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fwhat-can-i-do-about-climate-change%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%2010%20Years%20Of%20Modi's%20Foreign%20Policy%20-%20Aspiration%20Meets%20Self-Assurance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fkjvag4r8_g20-modi-1200_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20day%20might%20be%20a%20long%20time%20in%20politics%2C%20but%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F9-ways-indias-foreign-policy-has-evolved-in-9-years-4116701%5C%22%3Eforeign%20policy%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20a%20decade%20is%20usually%20not%20long%20enough%20to%20merit%20a%20serious%20appraisal.%20The%20last%20decade%2C%20however%2C%20has%20witnessed%20a%20phenomenal%20change%20in%20both%20the%20scale%20and%20the%20scope%20of%20global%20politics.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20politics%20in%20India%20has%20undergone%20a%20tectonic%20shift%20too.%20Inevitably%20then%2C%20India's%20foreign%20policy%20was%20bound%20to%20be%20affected%20as%20well.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20that.%20Beyond%20global%20shifts%2C%20it%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-9-years-of-pm-modi-a-look-at-indias-meteoric-rise-in-global-affairs-4043417%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%3C%2Fa%3E%20personal%20involvement%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-explains-how-government-functions-under-captain-modi-3832024%5C%22%3Erealm%20of%20external%20relations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20accorded%20India%20a%20unique%20place%20in%20contemporary%20international%20affairs%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProving%20The%20Critics%20Wrong%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20forget%20that%20when%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20his%20critics%20had%20painted%20him%20as%20a%20provincial%20politician%20who%20didn't%20have%20adequate%20engagement%20with%20foreign%20policy.%20His%20'Hindu%20nationalist'%20credentials%20were%20deemed%20to%20be%20a%20liability%20that%20would%20constrain%20India's%20outreach%20to%20the%20Islamic%20world%2C%20in%20particular.%20But%20Modi%20has%20managed%20to%20keep%20both%20his%20detractors%20as%20well%20as%20his%20supporters%20on%20tenterhooks%20by%20following%20a%20pragmatic%20foreign%20policy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-first-at-the-core-on-governments-foreign-policy-says-pm-modi-1441127%5C%22%3Ekeeping%20the%20'India%20first'%20mantra%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20its%20core.%20Right%20from%20the%20time%20he%20surprised%20everyone%20by%20inviting%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-years-of-narendra-modi-government-big-push-to-recast-foreign-policy-1704317%5C%22%3ESouth%20Asian%20nations%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20his%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20in%202014%2C%20to%20the%20current%20day%2C%20when%20he%20is%20set%20to%20visit%20Bhutan%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20gruelling%20election%20campaign%2C%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20has%20been%20'Modi-fied'%20in%20ways%20that%20were%20not%20expected%20when%20Modi%20took%20the%20reins%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20India's%20emergence%20as%20the%20centrepiece%20of%20contemporary%20global%20political%20discourse%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20with%20the%20structural%20changes%20shaping%20the%20international%20order.%20The%20shifting%20balance%20of%20power%20and%20growing%20disillusionment%20with%20China%20in%20the%20West%20has%20focused%20the%20world's%20attention%20on%20India%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20India's%20favourable%20demographics%2C%20its%20position%20as%20an%20attractive%20alternative%20to%20China%2C%20and%20its%20centrality%20in%20the%20key%20strategic%20geography%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20have%20together%20contributed%20to%20making%20this%20India's%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETowards%20Being%20A%20'Rule-Shaper'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20also%20changed%20is%20New%20Delhi's%20growing%20willingness%20to%20be%20more%20proactive%20on%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20which%20is%20in%20line%20with%20its%20aim%20of%20taking%20on%20the%20role%20of%20a%20'rule-shaper'.%20Modi's%20diplomacy%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20has%20managed%20to%20give%20wings%20to%20India's%20aspirations%20of%20playing%20a%20larger%20international%20role.%20Consequently%2C%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20has%20made%20the%20most%20of%20this%20inflexion%20point%20in%20world%20affairs.%20In%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20India's%20image%20of%20being%20a%20perpetual%20naysayer%20in%20global%20politics%20has%20changed%20to%20a%20nation%20that%20is%20more%20than%20willing%20to%20contribute%20to%20global%20governance.%20Just%20last%20week%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20rescue%20of%20a%20commercial%20ship%20that%20had%20been%20hijacked%20by%20pirates%20off%20Somalia's%20coast%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20Indian%20policymakers%20today%20are%20ready%20and%20willing%20to%20assume%20operational%20burdens%20in%20order%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20commercial%20shipping%20as%20well%20as%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20in%20strategically%20vital%20waterways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20artificial%20divide%20between%20the%20domestic%20and%20the%20foreign%20also%20seems%20to%20have%20faded%20under%20Modi.%20India's%20key%20priority%20remains%20its%20domestic%20developmental%20transformation%2C%20and%20for%20that%2C%20what's%20needed%20is%20an%20all-hands-on-deck%20approach.%20Indian%20diplomacy%2C%20too%2C%20is%20geared%20towards%20harnessing%20the%20country's%20developmental%20aspirations.%20This%20has%20brought%20about%20an%20inherent%20pragmatism%20in%20New%20Delhi's%20external%20outreach%2C%20wherein%20though%20partnerships%20have%20become%20key%2C%20India's%20needs%2C%20and%20not%20ideologies%2C%20determine%20the%20contours%20of%20its%20engagements.%20From%20building%20robust%20ties%20with%20the%20West%20to%20sustaining%20an%20important%20partnership%20with%20Russia%20through%20the%20tricky%20landscape%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20crisis%2C%20India%20has%20managed%20to%20insulate%20its%20global%20engagement%20from%20the%20growing%20turbulence%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Neighbourhood%20First'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government's%20regional%20outlook%20under%20the%20%26quot%3BNeighbourhood%20First%26quot%3B%20approach%20has%20sought%20to%20promote%20regional%20stability%20and%20prosperity%2C%20recognising%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20secure%20and%20cooperative%20neighbourhood%20for%20India's%20overall%20development%20and%20security.%20The%20focus%20of%20New%20Delhi's%20South%20Asia%20policy%20has%20shifted%20from%20its%20fixation%20with%20Pakistan%20to%20the%20more%20productive%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20maritime%20geography%2C%20which%20lends%20itself%20to%20a%20more%20organic%20connect%20between%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%20This%20permanent%20de-hyphenation%20of%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20is%20perhaps%20the%20single%20most%20important%20achievement%20of%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20allowing%20New%20Delhi%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20real%20strategic%20challenge%3A%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20had%20initially%20started%20off%20by%20reaching%20out%20to%20China%20so%20as%20to%20manage%20its%20rise%20through%20diplomatic%20engagement.%20Beijing%2C%20however%2C%20had%20other%20plans.%20India's%20stance%20after%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20crisis%20of%202020%2C%20that%20Sino-Indian%20relations%20cannot%20be%20normal%20unless%20the%20border%20situation%20is%20resolved%2C%20is%20audacious%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20going%20back%20on%20that.%20India's%20growing%20footprint%20in%20East%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20and%20its%20inclination%20to%20shape%20the%20strategic%20contours%20of%20the%20wider%20Indo-Pacific%20underscore%20a%20new%20reality%3A%20New%20Delhi%20will%20not%20be%20diffident%20as%20it%20seeks%20a%20greater%20regional%20and%20global%20role%20for%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDropping%20The%20Ideological%20Baggage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20not%20been%20averse%20to%20challenging%20adversaries%20and%20courting%20friends%2C%20and%20it%20has%20done%20these%20things%20without%20the%20ideological%20baggage%20of%20the%20past.%20From%20being%20the%20only%20global%20power%20to%20challenge%20Xi%20Jinping's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20as%20far%20back%20as%202014%2C%20responding%20to%20Chinese%20military%20aggression%20with%20a%20strong%20military%20pushback%2C%20trying%20to%20work%20with%20the%20US%20without%20entering%20into%20the%20full%20embrace%20of%20an%20alliance%2C%20to%20engaging%20the%20West%20for%20building%20domestic%20capacities%2C%20India%20has%20been%20pragmatic%20to%20the%20core%20and%20willing%20to%20use%20the%20extant%20balance%20of%20power%20to%20its%20advantage.%20India's%20focus%20today%20is%20on%20enhancing%20its%20capabilities%20in%20every%20possible%20sector%2C%20and%20that%20allows%20for%20a%20more%20clear-eyed%20engagement%20with%20its%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Responsible%20Stakeholder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%2C%20which%20has%20been%20more%20used%20to%20a%20pontificating%20India%20of%20the%20past%2C%20today%20hears%20an%20Indian%20voice%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20that%20is%20capable%20of%20articulating%20a%20narrative%20of%20a%20responsible%20stakeholder%2C%20which%2C%20despite%20being%20firmly%20steeped%20in%20its%20own%20ethos%2C%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20shirk%20global%20commitments.%20New%20Delhi%20led%20the%20way%20in%20shaping%20the%20regional%20response%20to%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20which%20then%20became%20global%20in%20scope.%20The%20Indian%20initiative%20to%20support%20its%20neighbours%20with%20critical%20supplies%20of%20medicines%20and%20later%20vaccines%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Vaccine%20Maitri%20initiative%20was%20a%20reflection%20of%20a%20new%20confidence%20in%20India%20that%20it%20can%20offer%20solutions%20to%20global%20problems.%20India's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-on-indias-g20-presidency-says-india-achieved-the-extraordinary-during-its-g20-presidency-4619752%5C%22%3EG-20%20presidency%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20only%20a%20recent%20example%20of%20how%20Modi's%20leadership%20on%20the%20international%20front%20has%20made%20a%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20challenging%20time%20in%20global%20politics%2C%20but%20Modi%20has%20given%20India%20a%20unique%20and%20special%20voice%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%20More%20than%20any%20other%20major%20power%20today%2C%20Indians%20view%20their%20future%20in%20aspirational%20terms%2C%20and%20that%20is%20shaping%20their%20domestic%20as%20well%20as%20foreign%20engagements.%20Modi%20has%20been%20successful%20not%20only%20in%20tapping%20into%20that%20sentiment%20effectively%2C%20but%20also%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20shaping%20that%20aspiration%20into%20his%20own%20image.%20And%20that's%20a%20formidable%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20books%20include%20'India%20and%20the%20Gulf%3A%20Theoretical%20Perspectives%20and%20Policy%20Shifts'%20(Cambridge%20University%20Press)%20and%20'Politics%20and%20Geopolitics%3A%20Decoding%20India's%20Neighbourhood%20Challenge'%20(Rupa)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711005120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fkjvag4r8_g20-modi-1200_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F10-years-of-modis-foreign-policy-aspiration-meets-self-assurance-5281335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%2C%20which%20has%20been%20more%20used%20to%20a%20pontificating%20India%20of%20the%20past%2C%20today%20hears%20an%20Indian%20voice%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20that%20is%20capable%20of%20articulating%20a%20narrative%20of%20a%20responsible%20stakeholder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F10-years-of-modis-foreign-policy-aspiration-meets-self-assurance-5