%20me.%20When%20I%20woke%20up%20from%20the%20anesthesia%2C%20he%20casually%20said%2C%20'Yep%20you%20have%20stage%203%20cervical%20cancer.'%20It%20turns%20out%2C%20it%20was%20not%20a%20fibroid%2C%20but%20cancer.%20I%20was%20misdiagnosed%20all%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Ms%20Pettway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20hearing%20that%20and%20immediately%20saying%20to%20myself%2C%20'I%20refuse%20to%20make%20an%20agreement%20with%20that%20diagnosis.'%20And%20so%20I%20didn't.%20Being%20told%20I%20have%20cancer%20didn't%20devastate%20me.%20It%20was%20the%20reaction%20of%20those%20close%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20she%20wrote%20alongside%20her%20family%20picture%20that%20an%20illness%20%26quot%3Balso%20changes%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20closest%20to%20you%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20countless%20hospital%20stays.%20To%20the%20financial%20strain.%20We%20been%20through%20it%20all!%20The%20girls%20are%20too%20young%20to%20understand%2C%20yet%20they%20noticed%20the%20changes.%20They%20would%20often%20ask%2C%20'when%20is%20mommy%20coming%20home%3F%26quot%3B%20Or%20'how%20come%20mommy%20keeps%20going%20in%20the%20ambulance%20truck%3F'%20Being%20wheeled%20into%20the%20ambulance%20and%20waving%20bye%20to%20my%20kids%2C%20only%20to%20see%20them%20crying%20for%20their%20mommy%20to%20stay%20home%2C%20broke%20me.%20And%20watching%20my%20husband%20break%20down%20in%20tears%2C%20was%20rough%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20influencer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20moved%20forward%20and%20did%20our%20best%20not%20to%20allow%20current%20circumstances%20to%20overtake%20us.%20It%20was%20definitely%20not%20easy%2C%20but%20we%20made%20it%20this%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Pettway%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECervical%20cancer%20is%20the%20fourth%20most%20common%20cancer%20in%20women%20which%20is%20caused%20by%20the%20abnormal%20growth%20cells%20in%20a%20woman's%20cervix%20or%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20uterus%20from%20the%20vagina%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO).%20An%20estimated%20604%2C000%20women%20were%20diagnosed%20with%20cervical%20cancer%20across%20the%20world%20in%202020%20and%20around%20342%2C%20000%20died%20from%20the%20disease.%20While%20common%2C%20cervical%20cancer%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20treatable%20forms%20of%20cancer%20if%20detected%20early.%20In%20later%20stages%2C%20the%20disease%20can%20be%20controlled%20through%20proper%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711005000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fr1ejppuo_jessica-pettway_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F36-year-old-beauty-youtuber-jessica-pettway-dies-of-cervical-cancer-after-misdiagnosis-5281362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20revealed%20in%20July%20last%20year%20that%20she%20had%20been%20misdiagnosed%20with%20fibroids%20initially.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F36-year-old-beauty-youtuber-jessica-pettway-dies-of-cervical-cancer-after-misdiagnosis-5281362%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F36-year-old-beauty-youtuber-jessica-pettway-dies-of-cervical-cancer-after-misdiagnosis-5281362%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F36-year-old-beauty-youtuber-jessica-pettway-dies-of-cervical-cancer-after-misdiagnosis-5281362%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Didn't%20Do%20Anything%26quot%3B%3A%20Brother%20Of%20Killer%20In%20UP%20Double%20Murder%20Surrenders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20a%20double%20murder%20sparked%20tension%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchilling-details-emerge-in-up-double-murder-killer-wanted-to-borrow-money-5273251%5C%22%3EUttar%20Pradesh's%20Budaun%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%