g%20on%20that%20(Shaw's%20form)%20with%20his%20strategy%20for%20the%20first%20six%20overs.%20If%20he%20can%20turn%20things%20around%20and%20compliment%20Warner%2C%20then%20the%20middle%20order%20is%20going%20to%20expose%20opposition%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20Hogg%2C%20who%20is%20a%20two-time%20World%20Cup%20winner%20with%20Australia%2C%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20on%20Tuesday%20appointed%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20Delhi%20Capitals%20for%20the%20upcoming%20edition%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20marking%20a%20wonderful%20chapter%20in%20his%20miraculous%20comeback%20saga.%20The%20keeper-batter%20missed%20cricketing%20action%20for%2014%20months%20after%20suffering%20a%20horrific%20car%20accident%20in%20December%202022.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20delighted%20to%20welcome%20Rishabh%20back%20as%20our%20captain.%20Grit%20and%20fearlessness%20have%20always%20dictated%20his%20brand%20of%20cricket%2C%20and%20not%20surprisingly%2C%20even%20his%20road%20to%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20wait%20to%20see%20him%20walk%20our%20team%20out%20once%20again%20as%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20new%20season%20with%20renewed%20passion%2C%20vigour%20and%20enthusiasm%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DC%20chairman%20and%20co-owner%20Parth%20Jindal%20in%20a%20media%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-hander%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Capitals%20pre-season%20preparatory%20camp%20in%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20ahead%20of%20their%20first%20IPL%202024%20match%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20March%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPL%20begins%20on%20March%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711004340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fnshmokdo_prithvi-shaw-bcci_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fprithvi-shaw-not-living-up-to-expectations-has-to-change-world-cup-winner-blasts-india-star-ahead-of-ipl-5278435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Away%20from%20the%20limelight%2C%20however%2C%20one%20promising%20Indian%20cricketer%20is%20facing%20challenges.%20He%20is%20Prithvi%20Shaw%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere%20Will%20Be%20Chaos%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20Refuses%20To%20Hold%20Poll%20Officers'%20Appointment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20order%20weeks%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20once%20again%20refused%20to%20order%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20law%20to%20appoint%20election%20commissioners%2C%20stating%20that%20doing%20so%20at%20this%20stage%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bcreating%20chaos%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20the%20observations%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20there%20are%20no%20allegations%20against%20the%20newly%20appointed%20election%20commissioners%2C%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%2C%20who%20were%20picked%20after%20changes%20were%20made%20to%20the%20selection%20panel%20under%20the%20new%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20say%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20under%20the%20thumb%20of%20the%20Executive.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20to%20the%20petitioners%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20presumed%20that%20the%20law%20enacted%20by%20the%20Centre%20is%20wrong%2C%20the%20bench%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20allegations%20against%20the%20persons%20who%20have%20been%20appointed...%20Elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner.%20Balance%20of%20convenience%20is%20very%20important.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20had%20been%20passed%20by%20the%20Parliament%20last%20year%20and%20subsequently%20got%20the%20President's%20assent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20law%20replaced%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20on%20a%20committee%20to%20pick%20election%20commissioners%20with%20a%20Union%20Cabinet%20minister.%20The%20committee%20now%20has%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20a%20Union%20Cabinet%20minister%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20raising%20concerns%20over%20its%20impartiality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20were%20picked%20by%20the%20panel%20last%20week%2C%20Congress'%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20had%20claimed%20he%20had%20been%20given%20212%20names%20for%20scrutiny%20the%20night%20before%2C%20and%20a%20shortlist%20of%20six%20names%20just%20before%20the%20meeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20had%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Mr%20Chowdhury.%20The%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20had%20said%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20should%20have%20been%20on%20this%20committee%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20new%20law%20had%20reduced%20the%20meeting%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bformality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Could%20Have%20Given%20More%20Time'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20the%20meeting%20had%20been%20rescheduled%20from%20March%2015%20-%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20supposed%20to%20hear%20a%20related%20matter%20-%20to%20March%2014%2C%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20was%20appearing%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20pointed%20to%20Mr%20Chowdhury's%20comments%20and%20said%20the%20shortlist%20had%20been%20sought%20on%20March%2012%2C%20but%20it%20had%20not%20been%20given.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhushan%20then%20said%20that%20the%20point%20being%20raised%20by%20the%20petitioners%20was%20on%20the%20procedure%20of%20selection%20and%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20Commission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20a%20point%20there...you%20have%20to%20give%20opportunity%20to%20examine%20names%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%20by%20giving%202-3%20days%20to%20the%20members%20to%20study%20the%20list.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711004220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F505hgpf_election-commission-press-conference_625x300_15_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-cant-put-on-hold-election-commissioners-appointment-5280878%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20significant%20order%20weeks%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20once%20again%20refused%20to%20order%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20law%20to%20appoint%20election%20commissioners%2C%20stating%20that%20doing%20so%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bcreating%20chaos%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-cant-put-on-hold-election-commissioners-appointment-5280878%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-cant-put-on-hold-election-commissioners-appointment-5280878%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-cant-put-on-hold-election-commissioners-appointment-5280878%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kung%20Fu%20Panda%204%20sees%20more%20than%20100%20%25%20jump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711003996000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108670176%2Cimgsize-32318.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentert