ie%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResearchers%20in%20Denmark%20are%20harnessing%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20data%20from%20millions%20of%20people%20to%20help%20anticipate%20the%20stages%20of%20an%20individual's%20life%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20end%2C%20hoping%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20the%20technology's%20power%2C%20and%20its%20perils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar%20from%20any%20morbid%20fascinations%2C%20the%20creators%20of%20life2vec%20want%20to%20explore%20patterns%20and%20relationships%20that%20so-called%20deep-learning%20programmes%20can%20uncover%20to%20predict%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20health%20or%20social%20%26quot%3Blife-events%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20general%20framework%20for%20making%20predictions%20about%20human%20lives.%20It%20can%20predict%20anything%20where%20you%20have%20training%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Sune%20Lehmann%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Technical%20University%20of%20Denmark%20(DTU)%20and%20one%20of%20the%20authors%20of%20a%20study%20recently%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Nature%20Computational%20Science%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Lehmann%2C%20the%20possibilities%20are%20endless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20predict%20health%20outcomes.%20So%20it%20could%20predict%20fertility%20or%20obesity%2C%20or%20you%20could%20maybe%20predict%20who%20will%20get%20cancer%20or%20who%20doesn't%20get%20cancer.%20But%20it%20could%20also%20predict%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20algorithm%20uses%20a%20similar%20process%20as%20that%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20but%20instead%20it%20analyses%20variables%20impacting%20life%20such%20as%20birth%2C%20education%2C%20social%20benefits%20or%20even%20work%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20is%20trying%20to%20adapt%20the%20innovations%20that%20enabled%20language-processing%20algorithms%20to%20%26quot%3Bexamine%20the%20evolution%20and%20predictability%20of%20human%20lives%20based%20on%20detailed%20event%20sequences%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20one%20perspective%2C%20lives%20are%20simply%20sequences%20of%20events%3A%20People%20are%20born%2C%20visit%20the%20paediatrician%2C%20start%20school%2C%20move%20to%20a%20new%20location%2C%20get%20married%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Lehmann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20disclosure%20of%20the%20programme%20quickly%20spawned%20claims%20of%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20calculator%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20some%20fraudulent%20sites%20duping%20people%20with%20offers%20to%20use%20the%20AI%20programme%20for%20a%20life%20expectancy%20prediction%20--%20often%20in%20exchange%20for%20submitting%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20insist%20the%20software%20is%20private%20and%20unavailable%20on%20the%20internet%20or%20to%20the%20wider%20research%20community%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EData%20from%20six%20million%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basis%20for%20the%20life2vec%20model%20is%20the%20anonymised%20data%20of%20around%20six%20million%20Danes%2C%20collected%20by%20the%20official%20Statistics%20Denmark%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20analysing%20sequences%20of%20events%20it%20is%20possible%20predict%20life%20outcomes%20right%20up%20until%20the%20last%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20predicting%20death%2C%20the%20algorithm%20is%20right%20in%2078%20percent%20of%20cases%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20predicting%20if%20a%20person%20will%20move%20to%20another%20city%20or%20country%2C%20it%20is%20correct%20in%2073%20percent%20of%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20look%20at%20early%20mortality.%20So%20we%20take%20a%20very%20young%20cohort%20between%2035%20and%2065.%20Then%20we%20try%20to%20predict%2C%20based%20on%20an%20eight-year%20period%20from%202008%20to%202016%2C%20if%20a%20person%20dies%20in%20the%20subsequent%20four%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Lehmann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20model%20can%20do%20that%20really%20well%2C%20better%20than%20any%20other%20algorithm%20that%20we%20could%20find%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20researchers%2C%20focusing%20on%20this%20age%20bracket%20--%20where%20deaths%20are%20usually%20few%20and%20far%20between%20--%20allows%20them%20to%20verify%20the%20algorithm's%20reliability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20tool%20is%20not%20yet%20ready%20for%20use%20outside%20a%20research%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20now%2C%20it's%20a%20research%20project%20where%20we're%20exploring%20what's%20possible%20and%20what's%20not%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Lehmann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20colleagues%20also%20want%20to%20explore%20long-term%20outcomes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20impact%20of%20social%20connections%20have%20on%20life%20and%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E'Public%20counterpoint'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20researchers%2C%20the%20project%20presents%20a%20scientific%20counterweight%20to%20the%20heavy%20investments%20into%20AI%20algorithms%20by%20large%20technology%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20also%20build%20models%20like%20this%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20making%20them%20public.%20They're%20not%20talking%20about%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Lehmann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20just%20building%20them%20to%2C%20hopefully%20for%20now%2C%20sell%20you%20more%20advertisements%2C%20or%20sell%20more%20advertisements%20and%20sell%20you%20more%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20to%20have%20an%20open%20and%20public%20counterpoint%20to%20begin%20to%20understand%20what%20can%20even%20happen%20with%20data%20like%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPernille%20Tranberg%2C%20a%20Danish%20data%20ethics%20expert%2C%20told%20AFP%20that%20this%20was%20especially%20true%20because%20similar%20algorithms%20were%20already%20being%20used%20by%20businesses%20such%20as%20insurance%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20probably%20put%20you%20into%20groups%20and%20say%3A%20'Okay%2C%20you%20have%20a%20chronic%20disease%2C%20the%20risk%20is%20this%20and%20this'%2C%26quot%3B%20Tranberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20used%20against%20us%20to%20discriminate%20us%20so%20that%20you%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20higher%20insurance%20premium%2C%20or%20you%20can't%20get%20a%20loan%20from%20the%20bank%2C%20or%20you%20can't%20get%20public%20health%20care%20because%20you're%20going%20to%20die%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20predicting%20our%20own%20demise%2C%20some%20developers%20have%20already%20tried%20to%20make%20such%20algorithms%20commercial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20web%2C%20we're%20already%20seeing%20prediction%20clocks%2C%20which%20show%20how%20old%20we're%20going%20to%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20Tranberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20them%20aren't%20at%20all%20reliable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711003140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fftedrcug_ai-generic_625x300_26_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-long-will-you-live-this-ai-algorithm-can-predict-when-you-will-die-5281160%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20in%20Denmark%20are%20harnessing%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20data%20from%20millions%20of%20people%20to%20help%20anticipate%20the%20stages%20of%20an%20individual's%20life%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20end%2C%20hoping%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20the%20technology's%20power%2C%20and%20its%20perils.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-long-will-you-live-this-ai-algorithm-can-predict-when-you-will-die-5281160%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-long-will-you-live-this-ai-algorithm-can-predict-when-you-will-die-5281160%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-long-will-you-live-this-ai-algorithm-can-predict-when-you-will-die-5281160%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trial%20Delay%2C%20Prolonged%20Jail%20Cause%20for%20Bail%20Despite%20Section%2045%20of%20PMLA%3A%20SC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25132016%2FSupreme-court4.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20orally%20observed%20that%20delay%20in%20trial%20and%20prolonged%20imprisonment%20makes%20an%20accused%20eligible%20for%20bail%20despite%20the%20Section%2045%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fs45-pmla-doesnt-bar-power-of-court-to-grant-bail-if-theres-delay-in-trial-justice-sanjiv-khanna-252861%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSupreme%2520Court%2520judge%2520Justice%2520Sanjiv%2Cincarceration%2520and%2520delay%2520in%2520trial.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20apex%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20on%20March%2020%20observed%20that%20the%20section%20does%20not%20bar%20an%20accused%20from%20bail%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20prolonged%20incarceration%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20something%20which%20flows%20from%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Section%2045%20has%20it%20that%20an%20accused%20can%20only%20be%20granted%20bail%20if%20the%20court%20is%20prima%20facie%20satisfied%20that%20he%20has%20not%20committed%20an%20offence%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20not%20commit%20it%20while%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20cited%20the%20judgment%20in%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20where%20Sisodia%20was%20granted%20liberty%20to%20apply%20for%20bail%20if%20there%20was%20delay%20in%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20further%20reported%20that%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%C2%A0was%20hearing%20the%20bail%20application%20of%20one%20Prem%20Prakash%2C%20who%20is%20alleged%20to%20be%20the%20aide%20of%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakash%20has%20spent%2018%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20told%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20S.V.%20Raju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20constitutional%20right%20is%20not%20taken%20away%20by%20Section%2045.%20It%20is%20very%20clear%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20ASG%20Raju%20said%20that%20Section%20436A%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20has%20it%20that%20an%20undertrial%20has%20to%20spend%20at%20least%2050%25%20of%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20to%20seek%20bail%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20delay%2C%C2%A0Justice%20Khanna%20said%20that%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Conly%20an%20enabling%20provision%E2%80%9D%20and%20does%20not%20disable%20the%20court%20from%20granting%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20bench%20did%20not%20grant%20bail%20to%20Prakash%20and%20adjourned%20the%20hearing%20by%20a%20month%20to%20ascertain%20the%20progress%20of%20trial%2C%20asking%20the%20court%20to%20expedite%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711003077000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25132016%2FSupreme-court4.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftrial-delay-prolonged-jail-cause-for-bail-despite-section-45-of-pmla-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apex%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20on%20March%2020%20observed%20that%20the%20section%20does%20not%20bar%20an%20accused%20from%20bail%20on%20