s%20issued%20by%20the%20assisted%20reproductive%20technology%20(ART)%20and%20surrogacy%20division%20of%20the%20health%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Health%20Research%2C%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20director%20asked%20the%20Punjab%20government%20to%20%E2%80%98look%20into%20the%20matter%E2%80%99%20and%20submit%20an%20action%20taken%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Charan%20Kaur%20was%2058%20years%20old%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20cited%20section%2021(g)(i)%20of%20the%20Assisted%20Reproductive%20Technology%20(Regulation)%20Act%2C%202021%20and%20mentioned%20that%20the%20age%20limit%20prescribed%20for%20a%20woman%20undergoing%20ART%20services%20was%20between%2021%20to%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20did%20not%20set%20a%20deadline%20for%20submitting%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharan%20Kaur%20and%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20father%20Balkaur%20Singh%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20baby%20boy%20through%20IVF%20treatment%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017)%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Bathinda%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20named%20the%20baby%20Shubhdeep%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20original%20name%20%E2%80%93%20evoking%20an%20emotional%20response%20among%20his%20fans%20that%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20would%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20letter%20was%20issued%20on%20March%2014%20while%20the%20baby%20was%20born%20on%20March%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20233821%2FShubhdeep-1024x683.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20233821%2FShubhdeep-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20233821%2FShubhdeep-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20233821%2FShubhdeep.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBalkaur%20Singh%20with%20the%20newly%20born%20Shubhdeep.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40iBalkaurSidhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ART%20law%20came%20into%20effect%20in%20January%202023.%20IVF%20treatment%20is%20meant%20for%20couples%20who%20face%20infertility%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20this%20news%20spread%2C%20renowned%20Punjabi%20singers%2C%20actors%2C%20and%20villagers%20at%20the%20Moosa%20village%20have%20been%20joining%20the%20family%20in%20their%20hour%20of%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20four%20days%20also%20saw%20many%20reels%20and%20videos%20on%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20songs%20as%20well%20as%20celebrations%20at%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoosewala%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20unidentified%20assailants%20on%20May%2029%2C%202022%20at%20Jawaharke%20village%20in%20Mansa%20district%20after%20his%20security%20cover%20was%20reduced%20by%20the%20Bhagwant%20Mann-led%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20in%20Punjab.%20He%20was%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoosewala%E2%80%99s%20father%20blames%20AAP%20government%20for%20harassing%20him%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%20came%20to%20light%20late%20on%20March%2019%2C%20when%20Balkaur%20Singh%20released%20a%20video%20on%20social%20media%20alleging%20that%20the%20Punjab%20government%2C%20through%20the%20local%20district%20administration%20and%20the%20Punjab%20police%2C%20was%20harassing%20him%20to%20furnish%20details%20of%20their%20IVF%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20shared%20by%20Singh%20on%20Instagram%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20asking%20him%20to%20furnish%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20documents%20and%20prove%20that%20the%20child%20was%20legal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20days%20ago%2C%20by%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20almighty%20and%20your%20prayers%2C%20we%20got%20our%20Shubhdeep%20Singh%20back%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20today%20morning%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20been%20asking%20questions%20and%20harassing%20me%20to%20provide%20documents%20of%20the%20baby%20and%20prove%20that%20the%20child%20is%20legal.%20It%20is%20my%20request%20to%20%E2%80%98CM%20sahib%E2%80%99%20to%20let%20the%20treatment%20be%20completed%20first.%20My%20wife%20is%20still%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hail%20from%20this%20place%20and%20would%20come%20whenever%20you%20call%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22pa%5C%22%3E%E0%A8%85%E0%A8%9C%E0%A8%BF%E0%A8%B9%E0%A8%BE%20%E0%A8%95%E0%A8%BF%E0%A8%B9%E0%A9%9C%E0%A8%BE%20%E0%A8%A1%E0%A8%B0%20%E0%A8%9C%E0%A8%BE%E0%A8%82%20%E0%A8%95%E0%A8%BF%E0%A8%B9%E0%A9%9C%E0%A9%80%20%E0%A8%AE%E0%A8%9C%E0%A8%AC%E0%A9%82%E0%A8%B0%E0%A9%80%20%E0%A8%B9%E0%A9%88%20%E0%A8%95%E0%A8%BF%20%E0%A8%B8%E0%A8%B0%E0%A8%95%E0%A8%BE%E0%A8%B0%20%E0%A8%87%E0%A9%B1%E0%A8%95%20%E0%A8%A8%E0%A8%B5-%E0%A8%9C%E0%A8%A8%E0%A8%AE%E0%A9%87%E0%A8%82%20%E0%A8%AC%E0%A9%B1%E0%A8%9A%E0%A9%87%20%E0%A8%A6%E0%A9%80%20%E0%A8%96%E0%A8%BC%E0%A9%81%E0%A8%B8%E0%A8%BC%E0%A9%80%20%E0%A8%B5%E0%A8%BF%E0%A9%B1%E0%A8%9A%20%E0%A8%B5%E0%A8%BF%E0%A8%98%E0%A8%A8%20%E0%A8%AA%E0%A8%BE%20%E0%A8%B0%E0%A8%B9%E0%A9%80%20%E0%A8%B9%E0%A9%88%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fb2y1kFYchn%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fb2y1kFYchn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Sardar%20Balkaur%20Singh%20Sidhu%20(%40iBalkaurSidhu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FiBalkaurSidhu%2Fstatus%2F1770139294964871168%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20visibly%20distraught%20Singh%20also%20gave%20a%20strongly%20worded%20message%20to%20chief%20minister%20Mann%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20deeply%20pained%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20in%20strong%20words%20that%20you%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20taking%20%E2%80%98U-turns%E2%80%99.%20Your%20advisors%20give%20you%20such%20advice%2C%20but%20I%20am%20an%20ex-soldier%20and%20I%20am%20not%20among%20those%20who%20would%20take%20U-turns.%20I%20will%20provide%20all%20the%20documents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20if%20he%20has%20violated%20the%20law%2C%20then%20the%20government%20can%20send%20him%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20am%20wrong%2C%20you%20can%20lodge%20an%20FIR%2C%20put%20me%20in%20jail%20and%20hold%20an%20investigation%20against%20me.%20But%20I%20will%20not%20run%20away%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMansa%20deputy%20commissioner%20denies%20allegations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20Mansa%20district%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC)%20Paramvir%20Singh%2C%20who%20denied%20having%20sent%20any%20officials%20from%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20seek%20documents%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20IVF%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DC%20said%20that%20the%20baby%20was%20delivered%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Bathinda%20district%2C%20whereas%20the%20family%20was%20based%20in%20Mansa%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20through%20the%20state%20government%20to%20check%20any%20violation%20of%20the%20ART%20Act%2C%202021%2C%20but%20whatever%20development%20has%20taken%20place%2C%20it%20was%20between%20the%20Union%20and%20the%20state%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20letter%20was%20addressed%20to%20the%20Punjab%20government.%20We%20have%20not%20taken%20any%20action%20against%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20doctors%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20Navjot%20Dahiya%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Congress%20leader%20from%20Jalandhar%2C%20said%20that%20as%20per%20the%202021%20ART%20(Regulation)%20Act%2C%20the%20prescribed%20age%20for%20a%20woman%20going%20under%20ART%20services%20is%20between%2021%20and%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20Charan%20Kaur%20was%2058%20years%20old%2C%20the%20notice%20was%20issued%2C%20but%20it%20is%20an%20open%20secret%20why%20the%20central%20%5BUnion%5D%20government%20was%20questioning%20them.%20Every%20day%20we%20receive%20more%20than%2010%20IVF%20cases%20in%20Jalandhar%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20IVF%20treatment%20taken%20by%20Balkaur%20Singh%20and%20his%20wife%20Charan%20Kaur%2C%20then%20they%20should%20question%20everybody.%20Why%20are%20they%20singling%20them%20out%3F%20It%20is%20sheer%20politicisation%20and%20harassment%20of%20the%20family%2C%20who%20have%20been%20through%20such%20trauma%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDahiya%20said%20that%20ideally%2C%20the%20government%20should%20question%20the%20medical%20practitioner%20who%20conducted%20the%20IVF%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fsidhu-moose-wala-a-complex-character-in-life-death-and-music%5C%22%3ESidhu%20Moose%20Wala%3A%20A%20Complex%20Character%20in%20Life%2C%20Death%20and%20Music%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20law%20too%2C%20a%20patient%20is%20considered%20innocent%20and%20ignorant%2C%20as%20they%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20medical%20treatment%20involved.%20It%20is%20the%20doctor%20who%20conducts%20the%20treatment%2C%20who%20should%20be%20held%20liable%20if%20a%20lapse%20has%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20wants%2C%20they%20can%20seek%20a%20discharge%20slip%20and%20medical%20treatment%20bills%20from%20Balkaur%20Singh%2C%20but%20harassing%20them%20is%20acutely%20shameful%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%20that%20if%20the%20couple%20took%20IVF%20treatment%20outside%20India%2C%20then%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20approach%20the%20concerned%20embassy%20to%20check%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20absolutely%20no%20point%20in%20questioning%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20newly%20born%20child.%20Moreover%2C%20sex%20determination%20is%20banned%20in%20India%2C%20but%20in%20foreign%20countries%2C%20they%20generally%20do%20sex%20selection%20in%20IVF%20treatment%20and%20inform%20the%20parents%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20reiterated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%2C%20SAD%20lash%20out%20at%20AAP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20strongly%20against%20the%20AAP%20government%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Punjab%20chief%20Amrinder%20Singh%20Raja%20Warring%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%E2%80%9CShame%20on%20you%20CM%20Saab%2C%20your%20government%20is%20asking%20for%20IVF%20treatment%20certificates%20from%20the%20parents%20of%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirstly%20no%20one%20should%20go%20and%20inquire%20about%20them.%20You%20want%20to%20disturb%20them%20in%20their%20moments%20of%20joy%3F%20Even%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%20atleast%20give%20them%20some%20time.%20He%20is%20an%20ex-%3Cem%3Efauji%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bsoldier%5D%20who%20has%20served%20the%20country%20at%20the%20border.%20He%20will%20not%20speak%20lies%20and%20will%20provide%20all%20the%20documents%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20wrong%20has%20he%20done%2C%20if%20has%20been%20speaking%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20AAP%20for%20justice%20in%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20killing%3F%20This%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20you%20will%20harass%20him%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarring%20asserted%20that%20the%20AAP%20government%20should%20not%20stoop%20so%20low%20and%20humiliate%20the%20family%20at%20this%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F24112045%2FFuT1rCsXoAEHY2S-1024x744.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F24112045%2FFuT1rCsXoAEHY2S-1024x744.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F24112045%2FFuT1rCsXoAEHY2S-300x218.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F24112045%2FFuT1rCsXoAEHY2S.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649974%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22610%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPunjab%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20politicians%20have%20accused%20the%20Bhagwant%20Mann-led%20AAP%20government%20of%20%E2%80%98harassing%E2%80%99%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20family.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BhagwantMann.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20a%20tragedy%20can%20happen%20with%20anybody.%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20parents%20have%20gone%20through%20a%20huge%20trauma.%20I%20want%20to%20reiterate%20that%20if%20the%20family%20was%20harassed%2C%20we%20will%20not%20tolerate%20it.%20We%20stand%20by%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20family%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Punjab%20assembly%2C%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa%2C%20also%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20be%20some%20limit%20to%20shamelessness!%20You%20and%20your%20government%20are%20not%20able%20to%20bear%20the%20happiness%20of%20the%20baby%2C%20whose%20birth%20was%20being%20celebrated%20across%20Punjab%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20kind%20of%20fear%20do%20you%20have%20from%20a%20newborn%20child%20that%20you%20were%20harassing%20Balkaur%20Singh%20and%20his%20family%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vocal%20critic%20of%20AAP%20and%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Sukhpal%20Singh%20Khaira%20also%20released%20a%20video%20on%20Facebook%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThousands%20of%20children%20are%20born%20through%20IVF%2C%20but%20I%20never%20saw%20police%20or%20administration%20seeking%20documents%20from%20the%20parents%20or%20harassing%20them%20on%20such%20a%20personal%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIdeally%2C%20CM%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20should%20have%20congratulated%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20parents%20on%20this%20occasion%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20pity%20that%20he%20was%20harassing%20his%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%20also%20lambasted%20the%20AAP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAD%20spokesperson%20Daljit%20Singh%20Cheema%2C%20who%20is%20a%20doctor%20by%20profession%2C%20shared%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20highly%20shameful%20and%20criminal%20act%20which%20has%20exposed%20the%20ugly%20face%20of%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Punjab.%20While%20the%20government%20should%20ensure%20proper%20treatment%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20mother%20and%20the%20new%20born%20baby%2C%20they%20are%20instead%20resorting%20to%20such%20arm-twisting%20methods%20to%20harass%20the%20grief-stricken%20parents%20of%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%20with%20false%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20actions%20undermine%20trust%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20prioritise%20the%20well-being%20of%20its%20citizens.%20It%20is%20high%20time%20that%20%5Bthe%5D%20people%20of%20Punjab%20should%20teach%20them%20a%20lesson.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP%E2%80%99s%20crisis%20management%3A%20Punjab%20health%20minister%20speaks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20defence%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20said%20on%20X%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20IVF%20treatment%20report%20was%20made%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCM%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20respects%20the%20sentiments%20of%20Punjabis%2C%20but%20these%20documents%20were%20sought%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20We%20urge%20Punjabis%20and%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20fans%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20rumours.%20We%20are%20sharing%20the%20letter%20issued%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Punjab%20health%20minister%20Balbir%20Singh%20congratulated%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%20parents%20and%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20harassment%20by%20the%20AAP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20letter.%20They%20plan%20cunning%20moves.%20This%20is%20the%20pathetic%20thinking%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%20Rest%20assured%2C%20we%20would%20not%20harass%20them%20in%20any%20way%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711001700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F29220428%2FUntitled-design-56-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhealth-ministry-sidhu-moosewala-mother-ivf-report-harassment-punjab-aap-govt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20health%20ministry%20cited%20the%20ART%20(Regulation)%20Act%20of%202021%20and%20sought%20a%20report%20from%20the%20Punjab%20government%20after%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%E2%80%99s%2058-year-old%20mother%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20baby%20boy%20on%20March%2017.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhealth-ministry-sidhu-moosewala-mother-ivf-report-harassment-punjab-aap-govt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%2