%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20who%20was%20appearing%20for%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20default%20bail%20plea%20filed%20by%20former%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20associate%20Prem%20Prakash%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20August%202022.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20denied%20Prakash%20bail%20in%20January%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20court%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20judges%20noted%20that%20Prakash%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20for%2018%20months%20and%20it%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20bail.%20The%20courtroom%20exchange%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20went%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20bail%20Mr%20Raju.%20Is%20it%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20interesting%20questions%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20ASG%20Raju%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInteresting%20okay%20but%20the%20person%20is%20behind%20bars%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20evidence%20tampering%2C%E2%80%9D%20ASG%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20come%20to%20us%20if%20he%20does%20any%20of%20that.%20But%2018%20months%20in%20jail%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710996731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17134928%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_01-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-criticised-eds-practice-of-keeping-accused-imprisoned-endlessly-without-trial%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTrial%20has%20to%20be%20begin%20when%20you%20arrest%20an%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-criticised-eds-practice-of-keeping-accused-imprisoned-endlessly-without-trial%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22a