0G.B.%20Pant%20Social%20Science%20Institute%2C%20Allahabad%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20loss%20in%20the%20key%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20despite%20its%20foregrounding%20of%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20shows%20that%20its%20social%20justice%20plank%20has%20not%20found%20any%20takers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20already%20seen%20what%20has%20happened%20with%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20social%20justice%20promises%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections.%20In%20my%20understanding%2C%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20influence%20the%20public%20in%20a%20big%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20north-south%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was%20conducted%20from%20October%202022%20to%20January%202023%20saw%20Gandhi%20undertake%20a%20walkathon%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20pitching%20a%20message%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ejodo%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20unity%20against%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20divisive%20politics%20and%20preaching%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emohabbat%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20love%2C%20the%20second%20instalment%20re%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-renames-rahul-gandhis-bharat-nyay-yatra-as-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echristened%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20mostly%20conducted%20by%20bus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20undertake%20the%20yatra%20by%20bus%20was%20mostly%20due%20to%20time%20constraints.%20But%20it%20limited%20the%20yatra%E2%80%99s%20mass%20reach%20%E2%80%93%20the%20very%20factor%20that%20saw%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-communications-team-social-media-makeover%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresurgent%20Gandhi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20a%20re-energised%20Congress%20in%20January%202023.%20Months%20after%20the%20four-month%20long%20yatra%2C%20the%20party%20saw%20dividends%20in%20its%20victory%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20cascaded%20onto%20Telangana%20elections%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20was%20an%20east-to-west%20yatra%20that%20went%20from%20Manipur%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20covered%206%2C700%20km%20touching%20110%20districts%2C%20100%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20and%20337%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20what%20was%20touted%20as%20the%20biggest%20mass%20outreach%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20undertake%20the%20yatra%2C%20just%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20even%20as%20seat%20sharing%20arrangements%20were%20not%20sealed%20with%20alliance%20partners%20was%20cr%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-communications-team-social-media-makeover%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eiticised%20by%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20month%20of%20the%20yatra%2C%20the%20TMC%20had%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fimportant-pillar-of-the-india-bloc-congress-after-tmc-reiterates-solo-act-for-bengal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20announced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20it%20would%20go%20solo%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20announced%20its%20own%20solitary%20act%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20JD(U)%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Facchoot-doesnt-mean-dalit-congress-politicises-everything-jdus-k-c-tyagi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erejoined%20hands%20with%20the%20NDA%3C%2Fspan%