al%20history%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20the%20manifesto%20itself%2C%20which%20has%20been%20given%20to%20Kharge%20for%20his%20authorisation%2C%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20document%20but%20roadmaps%20based%20on%20dialogue%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20party%20will%20fight%20the%20elections%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20these%20five%20Nyay%20resolutions%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20will%20touch%20every%20Indian%E2%80%99s%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EElectoral%20impact%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20guarantees%20now%20being%20pushed%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20its%20electoral%20impact%20remains%20under%20question%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20its%20poor%20performance%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20job%20of%20a%20political%20party%20is%20to%20win%20elections%2C%20the%20job%20of%20political%20leaders%20is%20to%20increase%20the%20vote%20share.%20The%20problem%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%20both%20its%20phases%20is%20that%20it%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20increase%20the%20vote%20share%20substantially%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rahseed%20Kidwai%2C%20visiting%20fellow%20at%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20and%20political%20commentator%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20the%20Congress%20won%2044%20seats%20with%2019.3%25%20vote%20share.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20it%20first%20brought%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fcongress-nyay-minimum-income-elections-2019%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eidea%20of%20Nyay%20in%20its%20manifesto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20bettered%20its%20tally%20to%2052%20seats%20but%20its%20vote%20share%20remained%20at%2019.5%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20objective%C2%A0%20of%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%20both%20phases%20would%20be%20to%20support%20the%20vote%20percentage%20from%2019%25%20to%20somewhere%20around%2025%25%20which%20would%20have%20given%20it%20political%20strength%20in%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kidwai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20we%20have%20seen%20is%20that%20in%20the%20assembly%202023%20elections%20it%20did%20not%20lead%20to%20substantial%20increase%20in%20vote%20share.%20So%20the%20promises%20they%20have%20made%2C%20need%20to%20be%20assessed%20how%20much%20impact%20it%20is%20making%20electorally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20Yatra%20has%20been%20questioned%2C%20with%20precious%20political%20time%20being%20lost%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20focusing%20on%20the%20polls%20and%20alliance%20building%20had%20come%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt%2C%20and%20then%20the%20Yatra%20which%20saw%20its%20fallout%20with%20the%20alliance%20unravelling%2C%20the%20challenge%20remains%20in%20direct%20contests%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20at%20least%20200-odd%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20most%20of%20them%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-has-no-option-but-to-recover-in-heartland-states-in-2024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enorth%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20down%20to%20a%20straight%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Congress%20becomes%20closer%20to%20100%20seats%2C%20there%20is%20a%20reduction%20in%20BJP%20seats.%20Its%20allies%20are%20capable%20%E2%80%93%20the%20RJD%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%2C%20and%20even%20Samajwadi%20Party%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20and%20take%20some%20seats.%20But%20it%20is%20the%20direct%20contests%20where%20Co