checked%20off%20a%20longtime%20dream%20and%20joined%20a%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20shareholder%20meeting%20session%20in%202023%20in%20Omaha%2C%20Nebraska%2C%20with%20Warren%20Buffett%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-mungers-best-business-advice-over-the-years-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Munger%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMunger's%20death%20in%20November%202023%20was%20another%20reminder%20for%20Goldstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20your%20bucket%20list%2C%20you%20can%20also%20only%20procrastinate%20for%20so%20long%2C%20because%20sooner%20or%20later%20things%20will%20be%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWriting%20a%20children's%20book%20about%20data%20science%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20jobs%20at%20Google%20and%20Meta%2C%20Goldstein%20often%20joked%20that%20the%20role%20of%20a%20data%20scientist%20was%20to%20apply%20children-level%20logic%20to%20things%20that%20appear%20complex.%20Upon%20retiring%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20write%20a%20children's%20book%20about%20data%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20have%20kids%20myself%20one%20day.%20So%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20very%20nice%20for%20them%20to%20have%20something%20to%20understand%20what%20their%20daddy%20did%20a%20long%20time%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20of%20Goldstein's%20passions%20is%20green%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20importing%20tea%20directly%20from%20Japan%20about%20three%20years%20ago%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20distributing%20it%20to%20friends%20and%20colleagues.%20Now%2C%20he's%20looking%20to%20establish%20something%20more%20structured%2C%20like%20a%20small%20online%20store%20so%20more%20people%20can%20access%20Japanese%20tea%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGetting%20another%20degree%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20younger%2C%20Goldstein%20read%20a%20trilogy%20of%20children's%20books%20about%20physics%20and%20Albert%20Einstein%2C%20which%20kickstarted%20his%20interest%20in%20numbers%20and%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20retirement%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20Germany's%20free%20college%20education%20and%20recently%20re-enrolled%20in%20university%2C%20this%20time%20to%20study%20physics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20now%20studying%20surrounded%20by%20freshmen%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%2C%20very%20strange%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20Goldstein%20structures%20his%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Goldstein%2C%20no%20day%20is%20without%20an%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wakes%20up%20at%207%20a.m.%20and%20leaves%20bed%20by%208%20a.m.%20He%20listens%20to%20financial%20news%20podcasts%2C%20prepares%20his%20green%20tea%2C%20and%20drinks%20it%20while%20taking%20in%20the%20local%20news%2C%20checking%20on%20his%20financial%20portfolio%2C%20and%20updating%20his%20personal%20expense%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20his%20day%20varies.%20He%20attends%20university%20classes%20three%20times%20a%20week%20and%20plans%20regular%20meetups%20with%20friends.%20He%20has%20added%20activities%20into%20his%20routine%20like%20swimming%20two%20to%20three%20times%20a%20week%20and%20walking%20between%2012%2C000%20and%2015%2C000%20steps%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldstein%20also%20schedules%20time%20for%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20several%20times%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20listens%20to%2020%20to%2030%20hours%20of%20podcasts%20every%20week%20and%20one%20audiobook%20every%20fortnight.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20list%20of%20TV%20shows%20and%20video%20games%20he%20saved%20for%20retirement%20that%20he%20is%20working%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20got%20into%20investing%20thanks%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-early-financial-independence-mindful-spending-investing-berlin-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ementee-mentor%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20teach%20more%20friends%20a