ce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChao%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chair%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20shipping%20company%20the%20Foremost%20Group%2C%20died%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Sunday%2C%20February%2011.%20Chao%20was%20also%20the%20wife%20of%20Jim%20Breyer%2C%20the%20venture%20capitalist%20founder%20of%20Breyer%20Capital%2C%20and%20the%20sister%20of%20former%20cabinet%20secretary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmitch-mcconnell-elaine-chao-marriage-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElaine%20Chao%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20married%20to%20Senate%20Minority%20Leader%20Mitch%20McConnell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20report%20from%20the%20Blanco%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20said%20Chao%20was%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Bgirls'%20weekend%26quot%3B%20at%20her%20ranch%20with%20a%20group%20of%20close%20friends%20when%20the%20incident%20occurred%20on%20Saturday%2C%20February%2010.%20The%20group%2C%20which%20included%20prominent%20female%20business%20leaders%2C%20attended%20a%20Pitbull%20concert%20in%20Austin%20on%20Friday%20and%20spent%20Saturday%20visiting%20the%20ranch%2C%20one%20of%20the%20women%20told%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20had%20dinner%20that%20evening%20at%20the%20guest%20lodge%20on%20the%20property%20and%20wrapped%20up%20at%20around%2011%3A30%20p.m.%20local%20time%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20which%20cited%20dinner%20attendees.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESeveral%20women%20told%20police%20they%20were%20all%20in%20good%20spirits%20during%20the%20get-together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFootage%20from%20cameras%20on%20the%20property%20showed%20Chao%20left%20the%20lodge%20and%20walked%20to%20her%20Tesla%20at%20around%2011%3A37%20p.m.%2C%20with%20a%20blanket%20wrapped%20around%20her%20and%20her%20cellphone%20held%20to%20her%20ear%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20A%20pond%20on%20the%20property%20was%20located%20between%20the%20guest%20house%20and%20the%20main%20house%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChao%2C%20in%20her%20Tesla%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangela-chao-foremost-group-death-tesla-gearshift-reverse-drowning-accident-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereversed%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20and%20over%20a%20limestone%20barrier%20wall%2C%20entering%20the%20water%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20Video%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efootage%20from%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecameras%20on%20the%20property%20showed%20the%20Tesla%20then%20floated%20to%20the%20center%20of%20the%20pond%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20around%2011%3A42%20p.m.%2C%20Chao%20called%20one%20of%20the%20friends%20she%20had%20just%20had%20dinner%20with%2C%20Amber%20Landeau-Keinan%2C%20and%20calmly%20told%20her%20she%20was%20in%20the%20pond%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20After%20Chao%20said%20her%20feet%20were%20underwater%2C%20her%20friend%20told%20her%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20calm%20voice%2C%20Chao%20informs%20Keinan%20she%20is%20not%20able%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20report%20said%2C%20citing%20an%20interview%20with%20Landeau-Keinan.%20%26quot%3BChao%20told%20Keinan%20the%20water%20was%20rising%20and%20she%20was%20going%20to%20die%20and%20said%20'I%20love%20you'%20to%20Keinan%20prior%20to%20the%20vehicle%20going%20underwater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phone%20call%20lasted%20about%208%20minutes%2C%20Landeau-Keinan%20told%20an%20investigating%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20friend%20who%20was%20at%20the%20property%2C%20Victoria%20Garcia%2C%20got%20into%20the%20pond%20and%20swam%20toward%20the%20Tesla%2C%20while%20Landeau-Keinan%20got%20into%20a%20kayak%20and%20paddled%20toward%20the%20car%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20which%20cited%20interviews%20with%20the%20people%20who%20were%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELandeau-Keinan%20and%20Garcia%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20law%20enforcement%20arrived%2C%20Chao%20and%20the%20Tesla%20had%20been%20in%20the%20water%20for%20about%2021%20minutes%2C%20with%20the%20vehicle%20submerged%20about%2025%20yards%20from%20the%20shore%2C%20police%20said.%20After%20several%20failed%20attempts%2C%20responders%20were%20able%20to%20remove%20Chao%20from%20the%20vehicle%20at%20about%2012%3A56%20a.m.%20local%20time.%20CPR%20was%20performed%2C%20but%20Chao%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20at%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20toxicology%20report%20later%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangela-chao-blood-alcohol-three-times-limit-death-tesla-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChao's%20blood-alcohol%20concentration%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%200.233%2C%20almost%20three%20times%20the%20legal%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreyer%2C%20Chao's%20husband%2C%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement%20to%20BI%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20heartbroken%20by%20this%20terrible%20tragedy.%20I%20am%20so%20appreciative%20for%20the%20remarkable%20efforts%20of%20the%20many%20first%20responders%20in%20Blanco%20County%20who%20did%20everything%20possible%20to%20save%20my%20wonderful%20wife's%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20BI%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20James%20S.%20C.%20Chao%2C%20Chao's%20father%2C%20and%20family%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAngela's%20passing%20was%20a%20terrible%20tragedy%2C%20and%20words%20cannot%20describe%20the%20family's%20profound%20grief.%C2%A0The%20family%20is%20grateful%20for%20the%20first%20responders%20and%20friends%20who%20tried%20so%20hard%20to%20save%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fangela-chao-final-moments-called-friend-tesla-sank-texas-pond-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710985527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb62d54af076d3cf924034%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22or