t%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20game%26quot%3B%20that%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20sitting%20still.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20pressure%20sores%20and%20things%20like%20that.%20So%20I%20just%20wasn't%20really%20able%20to%20play%20it%20as%20much%20as%20I%20wanted%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20chip%2C%20Arbaugh%20said%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20play%20the%20video%20game%20for%20several%20hours%20while%20lying%20in%20his%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArbaugh%20noted%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20restriction%26quot%3B%20so%20far%20was%20having%20to%20charge%20the%20implant%20again%20after%20going%20on%20a%20several-hours%20streak%20of%20playing%20video%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20play%20for%20eight%20hours%2C%20have%20to%20get%20off%20and%20let%20it%20charge%20for%20a%20while%20and%20then%20hopefully%20be%20able%20to%20play%20some%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArbaugh%20said%20that%20controlling%20Neuralink%20soon%20became%20%26quot%3Bintuitive%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20to%20move%20the%20computer%20cursor%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20only%20needed%20to%20imagine%20the%20cursor%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%20it%20was%20like%20using%20the%20force%20on%20a%20cursor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneuralink-first-human-trial-patient-quadriplegic-elon-musk-x-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710976956000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb65f0895d82203032d31c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneuralink-first-human-trial-patient-quadriplegic-elon-musk-x-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20Neuralink%20reveals%20first%20human%20trial%20patient%2C%20a%2029-year-old%2