hat%20will%20get%20a%20slightly%20longer%20cycle%20but%20will%20give%20definitive%20returns%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20of%20research%2C%20Keya%20zeroed%20down%20to%20cultivating%20the%20crop%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F34505%2Fraspberry-pi-kits-for-school-children-in-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblueberries%20and%20raspberries%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20cultivated%20largely%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Serbia%2C%20and%20Poland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20foreign%20crops%20adaptable%20with%20innovative%20methods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeya%20shares%20the%20major%20challenge%20in%20cultivating%20these%20exotic%20varieties%20was%20to%20make%20them%20adaptable%20to%20the%20Indian%20weather%20conditions.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20blueberries%20require%20cold%20winters%20and%20moderate%20to%20high%20rainfall%20throughout%20its%20growing%20season%2C%20raspberries%20are%20also%20suited%20to%20temperate%20regions%20with%20cool%20summers%20and%20mild%20winters%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20late%202019%2C%20Keya%20along%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20Vimal%20Salot%2C%20visited%20Mexico%20and%20Europe%20which%20had%20similar%20geometric%20conditions%20to%20Maharashtra.%20In%202020%2C%20she%20imported%20the%20first%20set%20of%20saplings%20adaptable%20to%20Indian%20weather%20conditions%20and%20harvested%20the%20first%20commercial%20yield%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-2-1710699316.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Keya%20installed%20low-cost%20tunnels%20in%20about%2080%20percent%20of%20her%20farm.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen