ia.com%2F313657%2Fbengal-human-trafficking-survivor-nasima-gain-started-utthan-collective-ilfat-to-help-victims%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20nightmare%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20group%20of%20boys%20returned%20to%20Sikkim%2C%20they%20were%20one%20short.%20Bijoy%20was%20missing.%20Frantic%2C%20his%20father%20called%20the%20only%20man%20he%20knew%20could%20help%20%E2%80%94%20Raju%20Nepali.%20Something%20of%20a%20hero%20in%20the%20Dooars%20region%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Raju%20is%20the%20first%20dialled%20number%20of%20any%20parent%20who%20is%20unable%20to%20trace%20their%20ward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20quick%20to%20calm%20a%20dishevelled%20parent%20down%20as%20he%20outlined%20the%20next%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313315%2Fassam-pallabi-ghosh-impact-and-dialogue-foundation-rescue-children-from-trafficking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20course%20of%20action%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Sikkim%20Police%20Department%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20assuring%20Bijoy%E2%80%99s%20father%20that%20he%20would%20help%20find%20Bijoy%2C%20Raju%20was%20already%20drafting%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20with%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20picture.%20A%20few%20seconds%20later%2C%20230%20people%20were%20notified%20about%20the%20missing%20boy.%20This%20included%20journalists%2C%20police%2C%20social%20workers%2C%20and%20lawyers%20across%20India%20who%20sprung%20into%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20few%20weeks%20were%20a%20busy%20time%20for%20the%20members%20of%20the%20group.%20As%20they%20discovered%2C%20the%20boy%20was%20lured%20by%20a%20drug%20peddler%20and%20taken%20to%20Bhagalpur%2C%20Bihar%2C%20where%20he%20was%20beaten.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20were%20flooded%20with%20messages%20for%20a%20ransom%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20see%20their